Twisted Postfix Delegation Policy Daemon


tools/ipdb_generate.sh : Created the GeoIP/ASN database
tools/p0f-scripts : daemontools scripts to run the p0f daemon

Uses: 
p0f > 2.0.8 - http://lcamtuf.coredump.cx/p0f.shtml
twisted

in Debian/Ubuntu:
aptitude install python-twisted p0f daemontools daemontools-run

Geoip database from http://freegeoip.net/
free ASN database from http://maxmind.com/
